559
00:28:47,480 --> 00:28:49,540
Mom, I'll go prepare your bath water.

560
00:28:49,960 --> 00:28:50,760
Wait.

561
00:28:52,720 --> 00:28:55,240
Since you were little, whenever something happens,

562
00:28:55,240 --> 00:28:57,040
you always hesitate to speak up.

563
00:28:57,480 --> 00:28:58,540
I know you too well.

564
00:28:58,760 --> 00:29:00,890
Don't keep me in suspense. Just tell me

565
00:29:01,720 --> 00:29:02,520
what's going on.

566
00:29:02,520 --> 00:29:03,320
It's nothing.

567
00:29:07,000 --> 00:29:08,800
Did you have a fight with Xinxin?

568
00:29:09,120 --> 00:29:09,680
No.

569
00:29:11,160 --> 00:29:13,020
It's a bit more serious than that.

570
00:29:13,520 --> 00:29:16,440
How serious could it be?

571
00:29:16,880 --> 00:29:17,920
At worst,

572
00:29:18,520 --> 00:29:19,650
you'd get divorced.

573
00:29:20,520 --> 00:29:21,380
We did divorce.

574
00:29:26,680 --> 00:29:27,680
You got divorced?

575
00:29:28,880 --> 00:29:29,680
Yes.

576
00:29:31,960 --> 00:29:33,760
Mom, your medicine is in the bag, right?

577
00:29:33,760 --> 00:29:34,240
It's fine.

578
00:29:34,240 --> 00:29:35,560
I'll get it myself.

579
00:29:35,640 --> 00:29:37,280
Here, drink some water.

580
00:29:38,320 --> 00:29:38,960
Xiaogang.

581
00:29:40,880 --> 00:29:43,560
Tell me quickly what happened.

582
00:29:44,080 --> 00:29:45,600
What did you do to Xinxin?

583
00:29:45,680 --> 00:29:47,560
I didn't do anything. It's not my fault.

584
00:29:47,560 --> 00:29:48,820
Then whose fault is it?

585
00:29:53,120 --> 00:29:54,520
Wan Xinxin cheated on me.

586
00:30:17,600 --> 00:30:18,440
Baby.

587
00:30:20,240 --> 00:30:21,200
You're awake.

588
00:30:23,280 --> 00:30:25,280
Mommy will get you something to eat.

589
00:31:00,800 --> 00:31:01,660
Strange uncle.

590
00:31:02,080 --> 00:31:03,520
You scared me to death.

591
00:31:03,840 --> 00:31:05,680
Oh my goodness! Why is it you?

592
00:31:06,080 --> 00:31:07,200
Why can't it be me?

593
00:31:08,200 --> 00:31:09,280
Well, um...

594
00:31:10,160 --> 00:31:11,620
The older guy didn't come.

595
00:31:11,920 --> 00:31:13,480
I didn't have time before.

596
00:31:13,680 --> 00:31:14,920
So I asked someone else for help.

597
00:31:14,920 --> 00:31:16,160
Now I've made time.

598
00:31:16,320 --> 00:31:18,000
They've already lent you the house.

599
00:31:18,000 --> 00:31:20,720
How can you still have the nerve to trouble them again?

600
00:31:20,720 --> 00:31:22,850
But he promised me he would come today.

601
00:31:40,960 --> 00:31:41,320
Mom!

602
00:31:42,560 --> 00:31:42,920
Mom!

603
00:31:43,320 --> 00:31:44,320
Mom, please stop.

604
00:31:44,600 --> 00:31:45,440
Come with me.

605
00:31:45,880 --> 00:31:48,680
Mom, we don't need to make a scene about this.

606
00:31:49,080 --> 00:31:50,640
Let's go home and talk about it.

607
00:31:50,640 --> 00:31:51,700
Listen carefully.

608
00:31:52,720 --> 00:31:54,520
If Wan Xinxin is cheating on you,

609
00:31:54,720 --> 00:31:55,980
I'll handle it for you.

610
00:31:56,160 --> 00:31:57,560
But if you're lying to me,

611
00:31:59,080 --> 00:32:00,480
you'll be in big trouble.

612
00:32:10,000 --> 00:32:12,680
Call Wan Xinxin right now and tell her to come back to work.

613
00:32:12,680 --> 00:32:14,010
You still want her back?

614
00:32:14,560 --> 00:32:15,320
I will not.

615
00:32:15,320 --> 00:32:16,000
Wan Xinxin.

616
00:32:18,520 --> 00:32:20,580
Hello. Who would you like to speak to?

617
00:32:21,480 --> 00:32:23,010
I'm looking for Wan Xinxin.

618
00:32:23,960 --> 00:32:24,800
Where is she?

619
00:32:25,080 --> 00:32:26,410
May I ask who's calling?

620
00:32:29,880 --> 00:32:32,210
Why aren't you eating? What are you doing?

621
00:32:33,160 --> 00:32:36,620
You look so distracted. Is my cooking poisonous or something?

622
00:32:36,680 --> 00:32:38,360
No, it's just... that weird guy.

623
00:32:38,360 --> 00:32:40,490
Why did he suddenly stop talking to me?

624
00:32:53,600 --> 00:32:55,840
Hello, Mr. Shi.

625
00:32:58,320 --> 00:33:00,450
You want me to come back to the company?

626
00:33:01,720 --> 00:33:02,840
Okay.

627
00:33:03,120 --> 00:33:05,580
Alright, I'll come back as soon as possible.

628
00:33:10,200 --> 00:33:12,400
What are you doing? What's going on?

629
00:33:13,360 --> 00:33:14,400
The she-devil called me.

630
00:33:14,400 --> 00:33:15,680
She wants me to return to the office immediately.

631
00:33:15,680 --> 00:33:18,560
She says there's something I must handle personally.

632
00:33:18,560 --> 00:33:21,560
See? The company can't function without your sister.

633
00:33:21,880 --> 00:33:22,400
Right.

634
00:33:22,640 --> 00:33:24,600
The Earth would stop spinning without you.

635
00:33:24,600 --> 00:33:27,000
Look at you being so important. Hurry up and eat.

636
00:33:27,000 --> 00:33:28,730
Heaven always leaves a way out.

637
00:33:29,160 --> 00:33:31,620
The universe wants me to rise from the ashes.

638
00:33:33,840 --> 00:33:35,370
You're not eating anymore?

639
00:33:42,360 --> 00:33:45,160
Sweetie, Daddy has to go work far away.

640
00:33:46,280 --> 00:33:48,720
Daddy, please don't go.

641
00:33:50,880 --> 00:33:53,200
I'll be good. Please don't leave.

642
00:33:53,400 --> 00:33:55,560
I'll miss you.

643
00:34:21,880 --> 00:34:22,400
Good morning.

644
00:34:22,400 --> 00:34:22,929
Morning.

645
00:34:24,560 --> 00:34:25,040
Xinxin.

646
00:34:25,040 --> 00:34:25,719
Hello.

647
00:34:25,920 --> 00:34:26,850
Why are you back?

648
00:34:27,040 --> 00:34:28,639
Mr. Shi asked me to come back.

649
00:34:29,480 --> 00:34:30,409
Where is Mr. Shi?

650
00:34:34,679 --> 00:34:35,480
What's wrong?

651
00:34:36,679 --> 00:34:37,540
What happened?

652
00:34:40,560 --> 00:34:42,159
Mr. Shi, I'm back.

653
00:34:42,639 --> 00:34:45,300
Wan Xinxin, you don't need to come to work today.

654
00:34:50,280 --> 00:34:50,639
Mom?

655
00:34:52,719 --> 00:34:53,199
No.

656
00:34:54,040 --> 00:34:56,520
Mom, why are you here?

657
00:34:56,880 --> 00:34:59,840
You shouldn't be calling me mom anymore, should you?

658
00:35:02,120 --> 00:35:03,450
So you know everything.

659
00:35:03,680 --> 00:35:06,740
Did you think you could hide something this big from me?

660
00:35:07,720 --> 00:35:09,650
I wasn't trying to hide it from you.

661
00:35:12,360 --> 00:35:13,890
I knew something was wrong.

662
00:35:15,280 --> 00:35:18,240
Alright. Mr. Shi gave you time off.

663
00:35:18,480 --> 00:35:19,940
Let's find a place to talk.

664
00:35:21,920 --> 00:35:22,440
Please.

665
00:35:22,640 --> 00:35:23,600
Thank you, Mr. Shi.

666
00:35:23,600 --> 00:35:24,130
Goodbye.

667
00:35:25,880 --> 00:35:26,610
I'm leaving.

668
00:36:00,360 --> 00:36:01,360
You had an affair.

669
00:36:02,560 --> 00:36:03,120
Ah.

670
00:36:03,680 --> 00:36:04,940
If you hadn't cheated,

671
00:36:05,280 --> 00:36:07,880
how could you have gotten divorced so quickly?

672
00:36:09,000 --> 00:36:10,720
Did Qin Gang tell you that?

673
00:36:12,440 --> 00:36:14,100
Since I'm sitting here today,

674
00:36:14,640 --> 00:36:16,370
I know exactly what's going on.

675
00:36:17,200 --> 00:36:18,200
I know my son well.

676
00:36:19,800 --> 00:36:21,730
He didn't like studying in school,

677
00:36:21,920 --> 00:36:24,120
and he doesn't like working as an adult.

678
00:36:24,280 --> 00:36:25,410
These are his flaws.

679
00:36:26,520 --> 00:36:28,650
But he also has two important virtues.

680
00:36:29,520 --> 00:36:31,440
Filial piety and loyalty.

681
00:36:32,720 --> 00:36:35,450
When he loves someone, he puts them on a pedestal.

682
00:36:35,720 --> 00:36:37,320
He chose to marry you,

683
00:36:37,320 --> 00:36:38,920
so he would never betray you.

684
00:36:39,720 --> 00:36:41,800
I just want to hear one thing from you.

685
00:36:44,560 --> 00:36:45,360
Auntie.

686
00:36:46,000 --> 00:36:48,360
You've come all this way across the ocean to find me,

687
00:36:48,360 --> 00:36:50,160
not just to criticize me, right?

688
00:36:51,400 --> 00:36:53,120
As for why we got divorced,

689
00:36:53,520 --> 00:36:54,760
you can ask your son.

690
00:36:55,760 --> 00:36:57,640
You probably wouldn't believe me anyway,

691
00:36:57,640 --> 00:36:59,040
and I'd just seem petty.

692
00:36:59,760 --> 00:37:01,760
Qin Gang and I are already divorced.

693
00:37:01,880 --> 00:37:03,360
It's all in the past.

694
00:37:04,280 --> 00:37:05,960
Since you've come to see me today,

695
00:37:05,960 --> 00:37:07,560
just say what you want to say.

696
00:37:08,040 --> 00:37:09,240
Where is my grandson?

697
00:37:09,320 --> 00:37:10,050
He's at home.

698
00:37:11,320 --> 00:37:12,400
He's so young,

699
00:37:12,640 --> 00:37:15,280
yet you leave him at home while you work.

700
00:37:15,440 --> 00:37:16,500
How can you bear it?

701
00:37:17,480 --> 00:37:18,040
I...

702
00:37:19,160 --> 00:37:20,220
No need to explain.

703
00:37:20,800 --> 00:37:21,530
Life is hard.

704
00:37:22,280 --> 00:37:24,740
Of course you need to earn money for formula.

705
00:37:27,480 --> 00:37:29,280
You don't need to say anything else.

706
00:37:29,280 --> 00:37:30,720
The situation is clear.

707
00:37:31,760 --> 00:37:34,520
You don't have the ability or the means

708
00:37:34,880 --> 00:37:36,680
to give my grandson a happy life.

709
00:37:37,280 --> 00:37:39,560
Therefore, you have to give him to me.

710
00:37:42,400 --> 00:37:43,330
Name your terms.

711
00:37:44,280 --> 00:37:46,400
Will you agree to any condition I set?

712
00:37:46,720 --> 00:37:47,780
Whatever you want.

713
00:37:49,800 --> 00:37:52,260
Then please don't come looking for me again.

714
00:37:52,840 --> 00:37:54,480
From the moment my baby was born,

715
00:37:54,480 --> 00:37:55,280
I told myself

716
00:37:55,400 --> 00:37:56,860
that he belongs only to me,

717
00:37:57,080 --> 00:37:59,080
and I won't let anyone take him away.

718
00:37:59,480 --> 00:38:01,600
Auntie, you just got off the plane.

719
00:38:01,760 --> 00:38:03,040
Please get some rest.

720
00:38:03,280 --> 00:38:05,200
I have things to do. I'm leaving now.

721
00:38:05,200 --> 00:38:06,260
Goodbye, Mrs. Qin.

722
00:38:07,080 --> 00:38:07,880
Wait a moment.

723
00:38:10,240 --> 00:38:11,700
You're quite impressive.

724
00:38:13,800 --> 00:38:17,320
Fine, let's not talk about this matter today.

725
00:38:18,560 --> 00:38:21,090
But I should have the right to see my grandson.

726
00:38:36,360 --> 00:38:36,890
This way.

727
00:38:41,840 --> 00:38:43,570
So you live in a place like this.

728
00:38:44,320 --> 00:38:45,800
To be honest, yes.

729
00:38:46,360 --> 00:38:49,090
And this apartment isn't even mine. It's rented.

730
00:38:49,800 --> 00:38:51,930
Where did you find a postpartum nanny?

731
00:38:52,240 --> 00:38:53,240
I didn't hire one.

732
00:38:53,800 --> 00:38:55,530
My family is taking care of him.

733
00:39:07,440 --> 00:39:08,040
What are you doing here?

734
00:39:08,040 --> 00:39:08,640
Hello.

735
00:39:09,680 --> 00:39:10,540
This is my home.

736
00:39:11,720 --> 00:39:13,040
Your sister had to go out.

737
00:39:13,040 --> 00:39:14,800
She asked me to look after the baby.

738
00:39:14,800 --> 00:39:15,930
He just fell asleep.

739
00:39:20,000 --> 00:39:20,600
This is...

740
00:39:22,600 --> 00:39:24,130
Seems I was right about you.

741
00:39:25,040 --> 00:39:27,370
So this is what you meant by 'your family.'

742
00:39:28,600 --> 00:39:29,600
No, ma'am.

743
00:39:29,600 --> 00:39:31,160
Where is my grandson?

744
00:39:37,120 --> 00:39:39,120
Who is this? She's so intimidating.

745
00:39:39,720 --> 00:39:42,120
Qin Gang's mother. Mrs. Qin.

746
00:39:43,840 --> 00:39:44,680
We're doomed.

747
00:39:44,680 --> 00:39:45,480
No, why did you

748
00:39:45,560 --> 00:39:47,160
choose this moment to show up?

749
00:39:47,160 --> 00:39:48,420
The baby is right here.

750
00:39:48,880 --> 00:39:51,640
I just came to bring some things for your baby.

751
00:39:51,640 --> 00:39:54,840
Your sister said she had something to do and asked me to watch the child.

752
00:39:54,840 --> 00:39:55,880
So here I am.

753
00:39:56,200 --> 00:39:58,480
I really can't explain this situation now.

754
00:39:58,480 --> 00:39:58,840
You.

755
00:40:00,480 --> 00:40:03,210
The food is ready. Are you going to serve it or not?

756
00:40:16,520 --> 00:40:17,880
This is my grandson.

757
00:40:24,760 --> 00:40:25,490
Sweetheart.

758
00:40:27,080 --> 00:40:29,120
I finally get to see you.

759
00:40:29,880 --> 00:40:31,320
Grandma is here to take you.

760
00:40:31,320 --> 00:40:33,560
We'll go live in a big house.

761
00:40:34,200 --> 00:40:34,880
Ma'am.

762
00:40:35,560 --> 00:40:37,090
What are you talking about?

763
00:40:39,920 --> 00:40:40,580
Who is this?

764
00:40:42,760 --> 00:40:43,160
He...

765
00:40:44,480 --> 00:40:45,920
He's my uncle.

766
00:40:50,280 --> 00:40:51,800
Ma'am, don't listen to her nonsense.

767
00:40:51,800 --> 00:40:52,800
I'm not her uncle.

768
00:40:53,040 --> 00:40:54,600
My name is Hua Ming.

769
00:40:54,880 --> 00:40:56,280
You can call me Xiao Huazi.

770
00:40:56,280 --> 00:40:57,440
Or you can call me Xiao Dengzi.

771
00:40:57,440 --> 00:40:59,700
I'm just here to serve her and her mother.

772
00:41:00,640 --> 00:41:01,640
Xiao Dengzi.

773
00:41:10,440 --> 00:41:14,000
Do you think living here is good enough?

774
00:41:14,680 --> 00:41:16,140
Yes, it's quite nice here.

775
00:41:18,280 --> 00:41:22,040
So it's just the two of you taking care of the baby?

776
00:41:23,240 --> 00:41:23,770
No, he...

777
00:41:24,120 --> 00:41:26,120
No, my sister usually takes care of him.

778
00:41:26,120 --> 00:41:27,120
Today she couldn't.

779
00:41:27,120 --> 00:41:28,360
I don't know what happened.

780
00:41:28,360 --> 00:41:30,090
He just came here temporarily.

781
00:41:30,840 --> 00:41:33,520
I've been through it all. Nothing escapes me.

782
00:41:34,440 --> 00:41:35,360
Temporarily?

783
00:41:36,760 --> 00:41:38,560
How could he possibly be here temporarily?

784
00:41:38,560 --> 00:41:39,360
If he were just visiting,

785
00:41:39,360 --> 00:41:42,220
he wouldn't be so familiar with this home, would he?

786
00:41:42,440 --> 00:41:44,400
Yes, I'm living in his apartment.

787
00:41:44,400 --> 00:41:47,440
So you're living together with him after all.

788
00:41:48,320 --> 00:41:50,600
No, please let me explain.

789
00:41:50,800 --> 00:41:51,600
We are just...

790
00:41:51,800 --> 00:41:52,520
Xinxin...

791
00:41:52,960 --> 00:41:55,220
You don't need to explain anything to me.

792
00:41:55,480 --> 00:41:58,200
I don't care about your personal affairs.

793
00:41:59,240 --> 00:42:01,440
But there's one thing I must make clear.

794
00:42:01,480 --> 00:42:04,200
My grandson absolutely cannot

795
00:42:04,480 --> 00:42:06,160
live in this kind of environment.

796
00:42:06,160 --> 00:42:08,890
The conditions here are inadequate in every way.

797
00:42:09,240 --> 00:42:10,300
You are his mother.

798
00:42:10,760 --> 00:42:12,520
You keep saying you love him.

799
00:42:13,000 --> 00:42:15,660
If you love him, you should give him everything.

800
00:42:15,720 --> 00:42:18,280
If you give him to me, he can have everything.

801
00:42:19,040 --> 00:42:20,520
I... give him to you?

802
00:42:23,040 --> 00:42:25,520
Wait, is he lacking food or clothes?

803
00:42:26,120 --> 00:42:27,050
Can you feed him?

804
00:42:27,320 --> 00:42:29,080
Won't I still be the one feeding him?

805
00:42:29,080 --> 00:42:30,200
What he needs most right now

806
00:42:30,200 --> 00:42:31,560
is me, his mother.

807
00:42:33,800 --> 00:42:34,930
If you give him to me,

808
00:42:35,160 --> 00:42:36,690
you'll still be his mother.

809
00:43:46,200 --> 00:43:46,720
Yaping.

810
00:43:47,920 --> 00:43:48,440
Jiang Qiaohua.

